Package jbgenerator.lib

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    JBContent
    This class stores the content of a SQL relation (= a table in the architect schema).
    JBGenerator
    This is the kernel of the library.
    JBProperty
    This class stores information of an attribute : its name, its types and its default value.
    JBType
    This class stores a type.
    JBWriter
    The function of this class is to write a JBContent in the java class format.
    SQLType
    The SQLType class is a holder for a (name, typecode) pair.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    JBGenerator.KeyManagementPolicy
    Precise how to choose the type of the property representing the imported key.
